{ Our new Chessable course is about beautiful combinations and attacking plans arising from the King’s Indian Mar del Plata variation.  We get the typical positions via @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1@@EndFEN@@  1.d4  Nf6  2.c4  g6  3.Nc3  Bg7  4.e4  d6  5.Nf3  O-O  6.Be2  e5  7.O-O  Nc6  8.d5  Ne7  9.Ne1  Nd7  10.Be3  f5  11.f3  f4  12.Bf2  g5  , or @@StartFEN@@r1bq1rk1/pppnnpbp/3p2p1/3Pp3/2P1P3/2N5/PP2BPPP/R1BQNRK1 w - - 3 10@@EndFEN@@  10.Nd3  f5  11.Bd2  Nf6  12.f3  f4  .  However, we can get these types of structures from almost all the other King’s Indian lines, and even from some other openings. The course contains 12 chapters with the most typical sacrifices and attacks, and the 13th one is dealing with all the other motifs.  The material is full of astonishing ideas, wonderful sacrifices, and unexpected defenses. That is why we mainly recommend this course for intermediate and advanced players, but the real admirers of the beauty in chess will find their pleasure too. Don’t worry, if the King’s Indian is not your main repertoire, these attacking plans and nice combinations are universal, they are useful for everybody.  Most of our positions are original, they were found by us analyzing the opening and middlegame positions. We didn’t want to repeat the well-known practical examples, which you can find in many books.  The King’s Indian is a unique opening in many ways. In most cases, the computer clearly underestimates Black’s attacking possibilities, so don’t trust the engines 100%. They can easily mislead us if we just rely on the immediate assessment of our silicon friend.  In many diagrams, there are some equally good alternatives to the solution. In most cases, we went for the beauty and sacrifices and not for the quiet normal moves. Anyway, there are a lot of candidate moves and in a practical game sometimes the less correct move gives you the chance to win in a spectacular way! The King’s Indian is very difficult and complex, so we can easily win a lost position by fiercely attacking the white king.  In our course, we did not choose incorrect moves. However, some mistakes are inevitable, but we have spent an enormous time to check everything with the engines. The KID is a good weapon for tacticians, who are happy to sacrifice material without calculating everything and enjoy the adrenaline rush. }
