25. h3
{ We have to blow up White's pawn structure, activating the light-squared bishop. }
25... Nxg2 26. Nxg2 { Now the bishop can join the attack with great effect! }
26... Bxh3 27. Rxg7
{ Do we bring the most important attacking piece into the battle or immediately take the rook back on g7? }
