[FEN "r1b3k1/2p3bp/p2p2r1/R1PPp3/1P2NP1q/3Nn1pB/6P1/3QBRK1 w - - 0 27"]
[SetUp "1"]

27. Qf3
{ Here we have a decision to make. Should we take the rook winning the exchange or eliminate the important defender? }
27... Bxh3
{ Obviously, it is much more important to take the only defender on the h-file.   27...Nxf1?  runs into  28.Bxc8!  Rxc8  29.Kxf1  , when White is suddenly much better. }
28. Qxe3
{ 28.gxh3  would be a huge mistake because after  28...Qxh3  , Black's attack crashes through. Now Black has opened up the h-file with tempo! }
28... Bxg2
{ Now ...Qh1 is hanging in the air, so White has to take the bishop. } 29. Kxg2
Qh2+ 30. Kf3 Qh5+
{ Unfortunately, there is nothing more in the position and Black has to give perpetual checks. }
31. Kg2 Qh2+ { With a repetition of moves. } *

