23. Bd2
{ White allows Black to get rid of both knights and deliver mate after ...Qh4. }
23... Nc6
{ Let's start with the one on e7! There are obviously other knight moves, but this is the most spectacular one. }
24. dxc6 { The time has come to sacrifice the other knight! } 24... Nd5
{ The most beautiful way, but there are certainly alternatives. } 25. Nxd5 Qh4
{ And mate will follow in a couple of moves. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
