26. Nxc7 { White allows a pretty combination, it is mate in three! } 26... Qh4+
{ What a wonderful queen sacrifice! } 27. Kxh4
{ Now that the king is finally on the h-file, let's bring another piece with a check! }
27... Rh6+ 28. Kg5
{ If the king goes to g3, then we can give mate with ...Rh3. } 28... Nh3# *

