22. Nxc7
{ Attacking the a8-rook, but Black has to focus on the kingside and attack the weakest pawn there. }
22... Ngf4 23. Nxa8
{ White was greedy enough taking the rook, the only question is where comes the next sacrifice? }
23... Nxg2 { Opening up the g-file and eliminating the last defender. } 24.
Nxg2 { Now the target is the knight, let's attack it! } 24... Nf4
{ With a mating attack. } *

