20. Bd3
{ White wants to open up the 2nd rank where the rook or the queen can defend it. }
20... Qh4 21. h3 { Now destroy White's defensive wall! } 21... Bxh3 22. gxh3
{ Bring the next piece into the battle! } 22... Ng5 23. Qc2
{ The queen is defending the 2nd rank and the h2-square. } 23... Qxh3 24. Qg2
{ Do we want to exchange the queen or save it and continue the attack without showing any mercy? }
24... Qd7
