24. gxh5 { Black was not afraid of gxh5, let's see why not! } 24... Nxd3 25.
Qxd3 { Activate your bishop! } 25... Bf4+ 26. Kh1
{ And the final step before mate: bring your queen! } 26... Qg5
{ Mate will follow shortly. } *

[Event "?"]
