23. g4
{ White wants to keep the position as close as possible, but a knight on g3 and a queen on h4 is a formidable force. }
23... Ng3 24. Qb2 { Would you take the rook on f1? } 24... Qh4
{ Of course not! The g3-knight is much more worth it than the pathetic f1-rook. }
25. Be1 { Clearing the way for the king to f2. } 25... Qh1+ 26. Kf2
{ Our queen has been attacked. Where would you put it not allowing the white king to go to g1? }
26... Qh2 { ∆ ...Bf6-h4 } *

