28. h3
{ The last hope is to create an impregnable blockade, but this cannot happen. }
28... Ne3 { All the black pieces are ready for the last assault. } 29. Nc2
{ Now the time has come for the final blow. } 29... Nxg2 30. Bxg2 Bxh3
{ With a dangerous attack, as Black has already two very strong pawns for the piece. }
