24. Ne3 Qg5 { The strongest attacking piece, the queen joins the knights. } 25.
Bc4 { Pribyl-Klundt, BL 1993. } 25... Ng3+
{ Followed by ...h4-h3, destroys the last defensive barricade. } 26. Kg1 h3
{ Black has a pleasent choice between ...h3-h2, or ...h3xg2 depending on White's answer. }
