{ White is far away from any breakthrough on the queenside, so Black can continue the attack on the kingside without any beautiful sacrifices. }
20... g3
{ This is the typical attacking move preparing ...Qh4 and mate on h2. In case of h2-h3, Black wants to sacrifice on h3 or g2 to blow up White's pawn chain. }
21. h3
