[SetUp "1"]

26. Nxa7 { This leaves the white king without any defenders. } 26... gxf2+ 27.
Kxf2 { The white king desires to escape via e1-d2, just don't let it happen! }
27... Qg3+ { Black cannot let the white king leave the kingside via Ke1-d2. }
28. Kf1
{ Black needs some more pieces since one queen alone usually cannot give mate. }
28... Nh4 { The idea is ...Ng2-e3. } 29. Nb5 Ng2
{ Planning ...Ne3# next. Black is winning. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
