[SetUp "1"]

25. Qf1 { White avoids the mate but loses material because now... } 25... gxf2+
{ The time is right to capture the rook! } 26. Nxf2
{ Give a check to the white king! } 26... Qg3+
{ White has to exchange the queens because if  27.Kh1  , then  27...f3  powerfully comes and immediately decides the battle. }
27. Qg2 Qxg2+ 28. Kxg2
{ Decoy the bishop to a vulnerable square and open up the f-file! } 28... f3+
29. Bxf3 { Now just save the hanging rook! } 29... Raa8
{ Black has an easy win in the endgame. } *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
