{ ∆ ...Qg3+ and ...h1=Q+, so White has got only one move.  31...Qg6  or  31...Qg5  with the same idea is equally good. }
32. Rh1 { Planning Ke1-d2 next. } 32... Qg3+ 33. Kf1
