24... Nxe4
{ In case of  24...Nxc2  25.bxc7  there are no immediate mating threats, White gets some practical chances at least. So instead of taking the queen, we again sacrifice a knight! However, now the queen  will get to h4 with lethal threats. }
25. fxe4 Qh4+ 26. Kg1 Qg3+ 27. Kh1 Nxc2
{ And now, when the black queen participates in the attack already, we can think about the material. }
