{ 25.hxg4  Qh4  26.Bxf4  hxg4  27.fxg4  transposes to the main line. } 25...
Qh4 26. Kf1
{ The king wants to leave the dangerous g-file. Nb6 is a well-known threat again. What can we do against it? }
26... Nf6
{ Certainly nothing. We just put more and more pressure on the g4-pawn and finally open up the g-file. }
27. Nb6
{ Here we go, there is the annoying double attack again. As in many cases, we just continue our attacking plan on the other flank. }
27... hxg4
{ Sacrificing the rook but winning precious time for opening up the g-file. }
28. Nxa8
{ Black is now a whole rook and piece down and the c8-bishop is hanging. How do we continue our attack? }
28... gxh3
{ Opening up the g-file is the most important achievement, and also the h3-pawn looks very promising. }
