{ Black has already sacrificed a piece and the a8-rook is hanging as well. On the other hand, the white king is in terrible shape, but how can the black pieces get even closer to it? }
25... Nxe4
{ The motif is a simple deflection; either the f3-pawn or the queen takes it, the consequences will be disastrous. }
26. Qxe4
{ 26.fxe4  is the simpler story,  26...f3  comes and two connected passed pawns on the third rank decide the battle. The queen has left the 2nd rank,  but the h4-knight hinders the mate on h2. }
26... Ng2
{ Not only opening up the h-file threatening ...Qh2 mate but at the same time closing the 2nd rank as well. }
27. Rf2 { Otherwise, a quick mate is coming. } 27... Qh2+ 28. Kf1
