22. Bb6
{ White clears the way for the king to f2, but the bishop had no safe square. A lot of pieces are hanging on the queenside. Do we deal with that? }
22... hxg2 { First, we open up both the g- and h-files. } 23. Nxg2
{ Now let's approach the king as close as possible. } 23... Qh2+ 24. Kf2
{ The time has come to look at the queenside. } 24... cxb6 25. Bxa8
{ White has an extra rook but the best defender, the g2-knight, will soon be eliminated. }
25... Rg6 26. Rg1
