27. Bf1
{ The natural way to protect the weak h3-pawn and prepare the defense of the 2nd rank. Now we want to renew the threat against the a7-rook. }
27... exf3 { Deflecting the queen from the defense of the d4-square. } 28. Qxf3
Bxb5 { Now the rook becomes unprotected. } 29. cxb5 Bd4+ *

