{ The white rook has already penetrated the 7th rank, attacking the e7-knight. Black's attack with the battery on the h-file seemingly has come to a dead end. We need some imagination to find a great attacking plan. Let's dream a little bit, ...Ng3 would be mate... }
22... Nfxd5
{ Black sacrifices the knight in order to clear the way for the other one to f5, threatening ...Ng3 mate. Another witty plan would be @@StartFEN@@r1b4k/2R1n1bp/p2p1n1r/1p1Pp1pq/PP2Pp2/5P2/1N2B1PP/3QNRBK b - - 0 23@@EndFEN@@  23...Qh4  24.Rxe7  Nh5  25.Re8  Bf8  , with a similar mating  threat on g3. }
