26. exf5
{ Passive defense doesn't help. On  26.Bg1?  h3  decides, and the same goes for @@StartFEN@@1r2q1k1/1pR1n1bp/pN1p3r/3Ppb2/1P2Pp1p/3N1Pn1/P1Q1BBPK/2R5 w - - 1 26@@EndFEN@@  26.Kg1?  h3  opening up the h-file. }
