27. fxg4 { Now we need to open up more files and diagonals. } 27... f3
{ Vacating the f4-square for the queen. } 28. Bxf3 Qf4
{ With a double threat of ...Qh2 mate and ...Nxf3. } 29. Bxg2 hxg2+ 30. Rxg2
{ White has to return the material. } 30... Nxg2 31. Kxg2 Qxc1
{ Finally, it is Black who has the extra piece. } *

