21... Nxe4 22. Rxc8
{ White wants to get rid of the dangerous bishop, fighting against the sacrifice on h3. Many pieces are hanging around, do we react, or continue our plan?   22.fxe4  loses to the well-known motif after  22...Qh4  23.h3  , when Black destroys the defense by  23...Bxh3!-+  . }
22... Qh4 { Black ignores the material losses and goes for the king hunt. } 23.
h3 { The rooks are still hanging, but Black has to be consequent. } 23... Ng5
