25... Nxh3 { No, of course not, we are going for the h3-pawn! } 26. gxh3 Qxh3+
27. Kg1 { Do we take the hanging rook? } 27... Nh4
{ No, not yet. First, we come to help our lonely queen with the knight. Black's attack crashes through. }
