Bxf3 gxf3 29. Ng4
{ White has to close the g-file, even if it is only a temporary achievement. }
29... Bxg4
{ If we have to decide on whether to take the c8-bishop or the a8-rook, it is highly recommended to take the bishop in most of the cases, since the light-squared bishop is one of the most important attackers. }
